# Environment Variables for Client

# For LOCAL development, use these:
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
VITE_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:5000

# For PRODUCTION (Vercel deployment), set these in Vercel dashboard:
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend-url.onrender.com/api
# VITE_SOCKET_URL=https://your-backend-url.onrender.com

# Instructions for Vercel:
# 1. Go to your Vercel project settings
# 2. Navigate to "Environment Variables"
# 3. Add VITE_API_URL with your Render backend URL (e.g., https://fullstackca.onrender.com/api)
# 4. Add VITE_SOCKET_URL with your Render backend URL (e.g., https://fullstackca.onrender.com)
# 5. Redeploy your application
